originalText: tch_payam
Start Element
payam
I will cull every single one of them! Tchort is evolution!
::The rassophore turns to you and silently watches you for a few moments, as if expecting you to say something first.::
Tchort is evolution. What can I do for you?
context.loc_tch_invasionStarted
context.npc_tch_payam_met
Tchort is Evolution, brother.
Hey there.
::His raises his head just slightly and answers with a slow, unhurried voice.::
::He waits for several more seconds before slightly raising his head and speaking in a slow, unhurried voice.::
Can you open the gate for me?
I need to leave the Institute building.
Are you in charge of opening the main gate?
I would like to ask you several questions about Tchortism.
So every time someone wants to enter or leave has to answer to you?
What does a cell about to undergo mitosis say to an interested investigator? "I hope I have your divided attention!"
I am looking for Rassophore Nevil; did he perhaps leave through the front gate?
You are supposed to greet a Tchortist with "Tchort is evolution," not "hey, there." Just so you know for future reference $(#brother/sister), or someone might take offense.
Evolution is Tchort, $(#brother/sister).
Tchort is evolution, $(#brother/sister).
::He nods.:: Tchort guide you.
What is the reason for your egress, $(#brother/sister)?

Yes, that is correct. All arrivals and departures are carefully monitored from this very room and if you, for instance, wished to leave the building, you'd have to use that intercom there and state the reason for your movement.
I am sorry, but I'm busy at the moment. My recommendation would be to either visit Eidein's Library or talk to someone from Propagation - Praepostor Amelia, for instance.

Well, I am most certainly not going  to question notability regarding their reasons for leaving or entering the Institute building; magnificent Tchort, no. But we can't have, for instance, a novitiate like you simply stroll in and out however he pleases without answering to anyone.

::He responds in his usual, slow manner of talking.::

Excuse me, $(#brother/sister)? Why are you telling me this?

Fights - rarely; shootings - never. Sometimes a brawl would break out, but mostly between inbreds who aren't worthy of our attention in the first place and had just arrived to cause trouble. Still, when these things do occur, we usually react quickly and deal with the situation.
Negative, he couldn't get past without me knowing it.
It's "Tchort guide you." Tchort guide you, $(#brother/sister).
Tchort guide you, $(#brother/sister).
I am Rassophore Payam and I am in charge of monitoring and security. What can I do for you?
Tchort guide you too, brother.
Of course, reading the Original Report should be your priority, if you haven't done so already. Anything else?
The procedures are there to be followed and respected, and if it is bothering you, you better adapt to it.
Excluding those, incidents are rare in the Institute courtyard. Visitors feel safe here, and that's how we intend them to.
I was informed and asked about the commotion regarding Rassophore Nevil's disappearance and I can confirm that he didn't pass through the main gate.

When a Tchortist greets you with "Tchort is evolution," you reply with  "Evolution is Tchort" and not "hey, there." Just so you know for future reference $(#brother/sister), or someone might take offense.
Could you just let me go without all these questions?
Right, but keep it short, $(#brother/sister).
A joke?
::He shrugs.:: Anything else?
tch-entry
Official business? On whose authority?
What kind of a private matter?
What for?
Please answer my question, $(#brother/sister); I'm simply following the proper procedure.
Principal Investigator Rista.
Principal Investigator Georgis.
Principal Investigator Schteff.

::Your statement is met with a statue-like stillness. The awkward moment doesn't last long, however.::

I know what mitosis is, I just don't understand why you think the "joke" you told me is so funny?
Yes, I have been informed of that, $(#brother/sister).
I don't know anyone called "Uh." In fact, I should warn you not to give false statements concerning your egress.
How long will you be out?
::He nods.:: I will note that. Tchort guide you, $(#brother/sister).
Everything you said has been noted. I will open the gate for you now, $(#brother/sister). Tchort guide you.
